{{Infobox software|name=Instagram|logo=[[File:instagram logo 2016.svg|100px]]<br/>[[File:Instagram logo.svg|196px]]|author={{hlist|[[Kevin Systrom]]|[[Mike Krieger]]}}|developer=[[Meta, Inc.]]|released={{Start date and age|2010|10|6}}|ver layout=|operating system={{hlist|[[iOS]]|[[Android]]|[[Fire OS]]|[[Microsoft Windows]]}}|size=|language=|language count=32|license=[[Software-ka gaarka ah]] leh [https://help.instagram.com/581066165581870 Shuruudaha Isticmaalka]|website={{URL|https://www.instagram.com/}}}}'''Instagram'''{{efn|Magaca inta badan waxaa loo soo gaabiyo sida '''IG''', '''Insta''', or '''the Gram'''}} waa adeeg la wadaaga [[sawir]] iyo [[Madal muuqaal oo online ah|muuqaal]] Maraykan ah oo adeega xidhiidhka bulshada ee ay aasaaseen [[Kevin Systrom]] iyo [[Mike Krieger]]. Bishii Abriil 2012, [[Meta, Inc]]. (ka dibna ''Facebook Inc''.) waxay ku heshay adeegga qiyaastii US$1 bilyan oo caddaan ah iyo kayd. Wuxuu u oggolaanayaa isticmaaleyaasha inay soo galiyaan warbaahin lagu tafatiran karo [[Shaandheeyaha sawirka|filtarrada]] oo lagu habeeyo [[Hashtag|hashtag-ka]] iyo [[sumadeynta juqraafiyeed]].  Qoraalada waxaa lala wadaagi karaa si guud ama kuwa raacsan horay loo ansixiyay.  Isticmaalayaashu waxay ku baadhi karaan macluumaadka isticmaalayaasha kale iyagoo isticmaalaya calaamado iyo goobo oo waxay ku eegi karaan macluumaadka isbeddelaya. Isticmaalayaashu way [[Badhanka jacel|jeclaan]] karaan sawirada oo waxay raaci karaan isticmaalayaasha kale si ay ugu daraan nuxurkooda quudinta shakhsi ahaaneed.<ref name=":9">{{cite web|url=https://www.socialmediatoday.com/news/instagram-stories-is-now-being-used-by-500-million-people-daily/547270/|title=Instagram Stories is Now Being Used by 500 Million People Daily|website=Social Media Today|access-date=April 16, 2019}}</ref>

Adeeggu waxa kale oo uu ku daray sifada fariimaha, awoodda in lagu daro sawiro badan ama muuqaalo hal boosto ah, iyo muuqaal 'sheekooyin'—ah oo la mid ah mucaaradka ugu weyn ee [[Snapchat]]—kaas oo u oggolaanaya isticmaalayaasha in ay ku dhejiyaan sawirro iyo fiidiyowyo quudin isdaba-joog ah, boosto kasta  ay heli karaan kuwa kale 24 saacadood midkiiba. Laga bilaabo Janaayo 2019, sifada Sheekooyinka waxaa isticmaala 500  milyan oo isticmaale maalin kasta.<ref name=":9" />

Asal ahaan waxaa loo soo saaray [[iOS]] Oktoobar 2010, Instagram si degdeg ah ayuu caan u helay, iyada oo hal milyan oo isticmaaleyaal ah la diiwaan geliyay laba bilood gudahood, 10 milyan sannadkii, iyo 1 bilyan laga bilaabo Juun 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|title=Instagram hits 1 billion monthly users, up from 800M in September|url=https://social.techcrunch.com/2018/06/20/instagram-1-billion-users/|access-date=2020-10-23|website=TechCrunch|language=en-US}}</ref> Nooca [[Android]] waxa la sii daayay Abriil 2012. Laga bilaabo Oktoobar 2015, in ka badan 40 bilyan sawir ayaa la sameeyay  uploaded.  In kasta oo lagu ammaanay saamayntiisa, Instagram ayaa noqotay mawduuca dhaleecaynta, gaar ahaan saamaynta xun ee caafimaadka maskaxda ee dhallinta, isbeddellada siyaasadda iyo is-dhexgalka, eedaha faafreebka, iyo macluumaadka sharci-darrada ah ama aan habboonayn ee isticmaalayaashu soo geliyaan.

Laga bilaabo Juun 2021, qofka ugu badan ee raacaa waa xirfadle kubbadda cagta [[Burtuqaal]] [[Cristiano Ronaldo]] oo leh in ka badan 300 milyan oo taageerayaal ah.<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|url=https://9to5mac.com/2019/12/16/apps-and-games-of-the-decade/|title=These were the most-downloaded apps and games of the decade|last=Miller|first=Chance|date=December 17, 2019|website=9to5Mac|access-date=December 17, 2019}}</ref>

Laga bilaabo Janaayo 14, 2019, sawirka aadka loogu jeclaa Instagram waa [[Ukunta Instagram|sawirka ukun]], oo lagu dhejiyay akoontada @world_record_egg, oo loo sameeyay ujeedada kaliya ee lagu dhaafinayo rikoorkii hore ee 18 milyan oo jeclaan ee boostada [[Kylie Jenner]].  Sawirku hadda waxa uu leeyahay in ka badan 55 million oo jeclaan.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2019/01/13/style/egg-instagram-most-liked.html|work=The New York Times|access-date=January 14, 2019|title=An Egg, Just a Regular Egg, Is Instagram's Most-Liked Post Ever}}</ref> Sawirka labaad ee aadka loo jeclaan yahay waa sawirka arooska oo [[Ariana Grande]] iyo ninkeeda Dalton Gomez.<ref>{{Cite web|title=The 20 Most Liked Pictures on Instagram|url=https://www.brandwatch.com/blog/most-liked-pictures-on-instagram/|access-date=2021-06-10|website=Brandwatch|language=en-US}}</ref> Instagramku waxa uu ahaa abka afraad ee ugu badan ee la soo dejiyo 2010-kii.<ref name=":8" />

